{"tid":934394,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"如真！如假！如果屌閪可屌自己！","createTime":"2018-12-09T08:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T14:15:17.000Z","uid":193893,"like":8,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"eff854233cd77a6f33afc8d9ef8fdf646829b616","tid":934394,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:46:42.000Z","msg":"如廣東話講開～yat飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n北方話講開～吃飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真有趣～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n奇怪卻發覺這～大學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每到晏晝都～聽到這新鮮～語～言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n閒埋～問句～屌左Lun-ch冇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每天要～屌一次～譚仔～woo~oh~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如真！如假！如果屌閪可屌自己！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我早餐屌碗沙牛～午餐屌米～夜晚屌屋企～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如痴！如醉！如果收工屌支大啤！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八點返歸個時～老母講句～唉～又醉啦屌你！<br />\n<br />\n概念來源：<br />\n食女=屌女，屌譚=食譚仔有咩問題<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/933788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/933788</a>"},{"pid":"fd93482d38c67cf76580e5d0e0224003e8f40c13","tid":934394,"uid":111157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:55:01.000Z","msg":"樓主屌左飯食左女未？"},{"pid":"f041d1eae8e2fa234b05c7f52d42f57f7e94f111","tid":934394,"uid":193893,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"fd93482d38c67cf76580e5d0e0224003e8f40c13","tid":934394,"uid":111157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T08:55:01.000Z","msg":"樓主屌左飯食左女未？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"屌左雞屎忽食左牛歡喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smi